          </li>
          <li className="my-1">Supports XML and JSON</li>
          <li className="my-1">
            By default <SpanBlue>JACKSON</SpanBlue> calls appropriate <SpanBlue>getter/setter methods</SpanBlue>
          </li>
        </ul>
